Bahrain GP: Allan McNish's guide to the perfect Sakhir lap
Ride on board Nico Rosbergs's 2014 Bahrain Grand Prix pole lap with Allan McNish describing what it takes to drive the perfect lap in Sakhir.Although Rosberg secured pole, it was his team-mate, Lewis Hamilton who won the race, in arguably one of the greatest races in Formula 1 history.This year's Bahrain Grand Prix will see Nico Rosberg trying to beat Lewis Hamilton for the first time this season, and break the current world champion's run of victories over the German.Available to UK users only.